<section class="suds-services">
  <div class="suds-services__wrap">
    <p class="suds-services__eyebrow">Choose the right mobile detail</p>
    <h1>Premium mobile detailing packages built around vehicle condition.</h1>
    <p class="suds-services__lead">
      Share your vehicle year, make, model, city, and photos if available for the most accurate recommendation.
      Suds Auto Salon comes to you for interior detailing, full details, protection work, and maintenance service around Seattle.
    </p>

    <div class="suds-services__grid">
      <article>
        <h2>Basic Detail</h2>
        <p class="suds-services__price">Best for upkeep</p>
        <p>For vehicles that are already in good shape and need a professional maintenance clean.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Light interior cleanup</li>
          <li>Exterior wash</li>
          <li>Glass, wheels, and wipe-downs</li>
          <li>Best as a recurring service</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="suds-services__featured">
        <h2>Signature Detail</h2>
        <p class="suds-services__price">Most popular first booking</p>
        <p>The best choice for most customers who want the vehicle cleaned inside and out in one mobile appointment.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Interior reset</li>
          <li>Exterior hand wash</li>
          <li>Wheels, tires, glass, trim</li>
          <li>Protection add-ons available</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article>
        <h2>Elite Reset</h2>
        <p class="suds-services__price">Highest transformation</p>
        <p>For neglected vehicles, resale prep, pet hair, family SUVs, heavy grime, and full inside-out transformations.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Deep interior focus</li>
          <li>Exterior reset</li>
          <li>Add stain, odor, or pet hair service</li>
          <li>Strongest option before selling</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article>
        <h2>Ceramic Coating</h2>
        <p class="suds-services__price">Gloss and protection</p>
        <p>For drivers who want stronger paint protection, easier washing, better gloss, and a finish that holds up longer.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Paint enhancement or correction</li>
          <li>Ceramic coating application</li>
          <li>Long-term protection</li>
          <li>Best for premium vehicles</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article>
        <h2>Maintenance Plan</h2>
        <p class="suds-services__price">Recurring clean vehicle care</p>
        <p>After the first reset, monthly maintenance keeps the car clean without letting buildup take over again.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Priority scheduling</li>
          <li>Monthly or recurring service</li>
          <li>Ideal after Signature or Elite Reset</li>
          <li>Monthly service options available</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article>
        <h2>Add-Ons</h2>
        <p class="suds-services__price">Priced by condition</p>
        <p>Add targeted services when the vehicle needs more than a standard package.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Pet hair removal</li>
          <li>Stain extraction</li>
          <li>Odor treatment</li>
          <li>Trim, glass, wheel, and paint protection</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="suds-services__cta">
      <div>
        <h2>Not sure what to book?</h2>
        <p>Send the vehicle details and Sam will recommend the right package before you book.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/pages/contact-us">Request a Quote</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .suds-services {
    background: #090909;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .suds-services__wrap {
    max-width: 1180px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 58px 20px;
  }

  .suds-services__eyebrow,
  .suds-services__price {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    color: #f2d36b;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .suds-services h1 {
    max-width: 980px;
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(3.4rem, 6vw, 6.4rem);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  .suds-services h2 {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  .suds-services__lead {
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 20px 0 0;
    color: #e8e8e8;
    font-size: 1.7rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .suds-services__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }

  .suds-services article,
  .suds-services__cta {
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .16);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 24px;
    background: #121212;
  }

  .suds-services__featured {
    border-color: #f2d36b;
    background: #1b170d;
  }

  .suds-services article p,
  .suds-services li,
  .suds-services__cta p {
    color: #e8e8e8;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .suds-services ul {
    margin: 16px 0 0;
    padding-left: 20px;
  }

  .suds-services__cta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 18px;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  .suds-services__cta div {
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .suds-services__cta a {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 48px;
    padding: 13px 20px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: #f2d36b;
    color: #090909;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 900px) {
    .suds-services__grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .suds-services__wrap {
      padding: 44px 18px;
    }

    .suds-services__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .suds-services__cta {
      align-items: stretch;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .suds-services__cta a {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Suds services funnel",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Suds services funnel"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
